page.title: 17INTERESTING PEOPLE
page.content: {Mrs. Wood ========= Her room is old fashioned. She has pictures of her family,chair arms with her own crocheted covers on and a few ornaments around the place. She says that she likes Burbage,enjoys taking a blind lady for a walk in her spare time and going to Womens Institute and Darby and Joan Club meetings.{ {Mr. Good ======== In Mr Good's front room there is an old fashioned sideboard with his books in it. He likes reading. He has collected a lot of pictures of his family and has covers on the chairs. In Mr. Good's spare time he goes for a drink at a Club and watches his favourite programme on the television.
